lead_paragraph: In a story sent Sept. 17 about a debate exchange on casino gambling between Republican presidential candidates Donald Trump and Jeb Bush, The Associated Press erroneously reported the name of Trump's spokeswoman. Her name is Hope Hicks, not Holly Hicks.
